ge-1248" src="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15823877_1397371246993809_1266358779_o-Kopiowanie-1024x650.jpg" alt="15823877_1397371246993809_1266358779_o (Kopiowanie)" width="640" height="406" srcset="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15823877_1397371246993809_1266358779_o-Kopiowanie-300x190.jpg 300w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15823877_1397371246993809_1266358779_o-Kopiowanie-1024x650.jpg 1024w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15823877_1397371246993809_1266358779_o-Kopiowanie.jpg 1046w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1249" src="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15824262_1397371260327141_2103745895_o-Kopiowanie-1024x650.jpg" alt="15824262_1397371260327141_2103745895_o (Kopiowanie)" width="640" height="406" srcset="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15824262_1397371260327141_2103745895_o-Kopiowanie-300x190.jpg 300w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15824262_1397371260327141_2103745895_o-Kopiowanie-1024x650.jpg 1024w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15824262_1397371260327141_2103745895_o-Kopiowanie.jpg 1046w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1250" src="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15857371_1397371286993805_1966731356_o-Kopiowanie-1024x650.jpg" alt="15857371_1397371286993805_1966731356_o (Kopiowanie)" width="640" height="406" srcset="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15857371_1397371286993805_1966731356_o-Kopiowanie-300x190.jpg 300w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15857371_1397371286993805_1966731356_o-Kopiowanie-1024x650.jpg 1024w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15857371_1397371286993805_1966731356_o-Kopiowanie.jpg 1046w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p lang="pl-PL"><span style="font-size: small;">Wykonalismy endoskopie w celu pobrania proby w kierunku badania histopatologicznego. Na filmie widzimy zmiane rozrostowa, ulokowana na wysokosci wpustu wnikajaca do wnetrza zoladka.<br />
</span></p>
