<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1240" src="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/I00001-1024x846.jpg" alt="I00001" width="640" height="529" srcset="http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/I00001-300x248.jpg 300w, http://blog.gkw.com.pl/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/I00001-1024x846.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
